{
    "stimuli": [
        {
            "name": "ch0_half_scale",
            "mock_preload": {
                "stream": [
                    0,
                    2,
                    0
                ]
            },
            "expected": {
                "raw": 512,
                "channels": {
                    "ch0": {"raw": 512, "tolerance": 2},
                    "ch1": {"raw": 512, "tolerance": 2},
                    "ch2": {"raw": 512, "tolerance": 2},
                    "ch3": {"raw": 512, "tolerance": 2},
                    "ch4": {"raw": 512, "tolerance": 2},
                    "ch5": {"raw": 512, "tolerance": 2},
                    "ch6": {"raw": 512, "tolerance": 2},
                    "ch7": {"raw": 512, "tolerance": 2}
                }
            },
            "note": "MCP3008 3-byte full-duplex frame: master sends 0x01 (start), 0x80|ch<<4 (sgl+ch), 0x00 (dummy). Slave replies rx[0]=garbage, rx[1] carries B9:B8 in [1:0], rx[2] carries B7:B0. stream=[0,2,0] places B9:B8=10 in rx[1] -> raw=(rx[1]&0x03)<<8|rx[2]=512=Vref/2. Stub is stream-proto with CS pulse (TXN_RESET) resetting idx each channel read, so all 8 channels see the same playback and return the same value."
        },
